{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9c6d99c6ec","title":"毛泽东关于整顿人民公社问题给刘子厚的信","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"db07b72349","index":0,"year":1959,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"46956991e6","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于整顿人民公社问题给刘子厚的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"ce1962c823","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"8d925b8323","type":"appellation","text":"刘子厚同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"195d00140c","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天谈得相当舒畅，相当好，感谢你们!一月改变整社的方针政策，与党大会的想法不同，是很好的。我觉得你们路线好，但是还有参考别省经验和做法的必要。山西一月决议极好，你们可以打电话叫他们送一份给你们，可能对你们有某些参考价值的。你们有一个整社六个问题的指示文件没有?应当有吧。我极想看，有的话，送一份送<给>我，两天内送到济南即可。我在这里有两三天住，来得及的。至祷至盼!","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"cfb2cf77ea","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"2494f97871","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"f8cd12298b","type":"paragraph","text":"印发各同志。此件很好，可作参考。注意看“第三，分配问题”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"},{"id":"88ca10ad85","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东1959年2月27日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec"}],"page":{"id":"2e752a4fd7","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9c6d99c6ec","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}